s performance and management as well as being creative\nHe manages his team with detailed and clear directions and reports up the structure in a timely and professional way. Ansari has enormous potential and his loyalty to his company and colleagues is commendable.", "recommendations/9/name": "Ansari Allauddin", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "Executive Chef at Malahini Kuda Bandos Resort Maldives.", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ansari-allauddin-40534131/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAaigQUBopcfuoBS_Wzk6-K7zsi22ATYVjc", "recommendations/10/context": "Chris worked with Juergen E. on the same team", "recommendations/10/date": "March 11, 2011", "recommendations/10/description": "I have worked with Juergen in various roles for over 7 years and throughout this time he has displayed a high level of professionalism and a constant, positive and energetic attitude to his work. Juergen constantly seeks to develop and improve all departments within his remit\nJuergen is a strong communicator with a focus on detail.He is well respected by his colleagues and subordinates and focused on meeting his targets\nJuergen brings knowledge and experience to whatever role or task he takes on", "recommendations/10/name": "Juergen E. Seidel (PMI/PMP®)", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "Technical Services / Design / Project Management & Pre-Opening Specialist", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/juergeneseidel/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMDMpcB-uB5yIkrfiCIjtwK-NL1wL-LKpo", "recommendations/11/context": "Chris managed Derrick directly", "recommendations/11/date": "October 31, 2010", "recommendations/11/description": "Derrick managed 2 Spas for Six Senses in Hua Hin using a valuable balance of genuine belief in and understanding of the Holistic elements of Wellness whilst combining this knowledge with a strong commercial application. He is a natural leader and dynamic team builder\nDerrick added signif